<author>Joy F. Patterson</author>
<title>Dette er dagen</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Dette er dagen
 dette er dagen
 som Gud har gjort,
 ja som Gud har gjort (2x)

[V2]
 Kom la oss fryde oss
 og glede oss i den (2x)
 dette er dagen
 dette er dagen,
 ja som Gud har gjort.

[V3]
 This is the day, this is the day
 That the Lord hath made,
 That the Lord hath made,
 We will rejoice, we will rejoice
 And be glad in it, and be glad in it.

[V4]
 This is the week
 Of the devil's defeat
 We will rejoice and be glad in it,
 This is the week
 Of the devil's defeat

[V5]
 This is the month
 of the Lord's triumph, of the Lord's triumph
 We will rejoice and be glad in it,
 This is the month
 of the Lord's triumph

[V6]
 This is the Year - this is the Year
 of Jubilee
 We will rejoice and be glad in it,
 This is the Year of Jubilee
 This is the Year of Jubilee</lyrics>
<key>D</key>
<aka>This is the day</aka>
</song>